    <section class="section-summary" id="sect-00006">
    <title/>
    <para id="para-00021">Net present value (NPV) is calculated by subtracting the present value of a project’s cash outflows from the present value of the project’s cash inflows. A project should be accepted if its NPV is positive and rejected if its NPV is negative.</para>
    </section>
